#rad
       sin(α+2kπ)=sin α
               |   π
 sin(π-α)=sin α|sin(-- +α)=cos α
               |   2
---------------|-------------------
               |   π
sin(π+α)=-sin α|sin(-- -α)=cos α
               |   2
#deg
        sin(α+k*360°)=sin α
 sin(180°-α)=sin α|sin(90°+α)=cos α
------------------|-------------------
sin(180°+α)=-sin α|sin(90°-α)=cos α